snippet.title: Nikola's Fate - Gameplay
snippet.description:
This game was originally created for "Marcos Game Dev Jam 3" in 2 days, in this JAM the theme was "Physics" so I wanted to do something fun and chaotic! Nikola's Fate came in 14th place standing out more in "Game Experience". :D

Play here:
https://williamjacobproductions.com/nikolasfate
